org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_Foundations.GRM

Interface Scheduler

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Resource
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GaCommHost, GaExecHost, SaCommHost, SaExecHost, SecondaryScheduler
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GaCommHostImpl, GaExecHostImpl, SaCommHostImpl, SaExecHostImpl, SchedulerImpl, SecondarySchedulerImpl

    public interface Scheduler
extends Resource
    A representation of the model object 'Scheduler'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Is Preemptible
    • Sched Policy
    • Other Sched Policy
    • Schedule
    • Processing Units
    • Host
    • Protected Shared Resources
    • Schedulable Resources

    See Also:
    GRMPackage.getScheduler()
